Date: Wed, 11 Jun 2025 12:03:06 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] remoteproc: Don't use %pK through printk
Precedence: bulk
X-Mailing-List: linux-remoteproc@vger.kernel.org
List-Id: <linux-remoteproc.vger.kernel.org>
